    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> lamb mince </strong>to a large bowl with your <strong>chopped shallot</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>curry powder</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Add 2/3 of your <strong>tamarind paste</strong> and 2/3 of your <strong>soy sauce</strong> (you’ll use the rest later!)</p><p>Add a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up (clean hands are the best way!) – this is your <strong>murtabak filling</strong></p>",
