    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add<strong> </strong>1<strong> roti </strong>per person<strong> </strong>to a baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Divide the <strong>murtabak filling</strong> between the roti[s], evenly covering the roti[s] and spreading the filling almost to the edges</p>",
