    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the filled roti[s] with the <strong>remaining roti[s]</strong>,<strong> </strong>then a piece of <strong>baking paper</strong></p><p>Top each tray of <strong>roti[s]</strong> with another baking tray (this will help to keep them flat during cooking)</p><p>Put the trays in the oven and cook for 15-18 min or until the lamb is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Malaysian-style lamb murtabak</strong></p>",
