    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>sambal oelek</strong> with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, the <strong>remaining tamarind paste</strong> and <strong>remaining chilli flakes</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Add 1 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 1/2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your <strong>sambal oelek sauce</strong></p>",
